GriefShare||<p><span>GriefShare is a 13-week support group for people dealing with the death of a loved one. Every session is "self-contained" so attendees are welcome to join at any point in the series. This series is designed to help you successfully travel the journey from mourning to joy. Workshop fee is $25 per participant, and is facilitated by Tom Dooley.</span></p>
<p>For more information, click <a href="/ministries/adult-education/griefshare/">here</a>.</p>